## Per-entry format

```
### <Family name>
Location: <path pattern, e.g. `{{ROOT}}/logs/**/*.log` or `{{ROOT}}/outputs/*.csv`>
Format: <plain text | JSON | CSV | binary | other>
Produced by: <what generates this — a script, a service, a job, a test run>
Cadence: <when it appears — per-run, per-day, on-error, manually>
Key signals: <what to look for — error prefixes, field names, anomaly patterns>
Notes: <anything else a diagnostic agent needs to know>
```

